            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
            <a href="https://spacet-release.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/img/blog/2023-10-04/mau-thiet-ke-toi-gian-651cda65c9649b0ef5c6f426.webp" target="_blank">
                <img src="https://spacet-release.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/img/blog/2023-10-04/mau-thiet-ke-toi-gian-651cda65c9649b0ef5c6f426.webp" class="d-block w-100 banner-img" alt="Design Image 2">
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
